helpText: `ban: words` - bans words after the `:`, use commas to separate words/phrases
`unban: words` - unbans words  after the `:` if they are currently in ban list, use commas to separate words/phrases
`list all:` - lists all currently banned words
`set timeout: number` - sets bot message tiemout in seconds
`play: kewords` - plays music from youtube related to keywords after the :, limited to 5 min videos for server load reasons
